.\" Man page for m88-qt.  Install with: cmake --install build --prefix /usr
.TH M88-QT 1 "@M88_PORT_VERSION@" "M88"
.SH NAME
m88-qt \- PC-8801 series emulator (Qt frontend)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B m88-qt
[\fIoptions\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B m88-qt
is a Qt 6 frontend for the M88 PC-8801 emulator on Linux.
.PP
Configuration and user data are stored in the current working directory when
\fIm88.ini\fR is present there; otherwise they are stored under
\fI$HOME/.config/m88/\fR.
.PP
ROM files must be placed in the \fIroms/\fR subdirectory of the configuration
directory, or loaded from a directory given with \fB--rom-dir\fR.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-\-scale " N"
Set the initial window scale factor.
.TP
.BR \-\-rom-dir " PATH"
Load ROM and rhythm WAV files from \fIPATH\fR instead of the default
\fIroms/\fR directory.
.TP
.BR \-d0 " FILE"
Insert disk image \fIFILE\fR into drive 0 at startup.
.TP
.BR \-\-config " PATH"
Use \fIPATH\fR as the configuration file (\fIm88.ini\fR).
.TP
.BR \-\-keyboard " TYPE"
Select keyboard layout (\fBjis\fR, \fB101\fR, etc.).
.TP
.BR \-\-arrow-tenkey
Map arrow keys to the numeric keypad.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.config/m88/m88.ini
User configuration (when not using a local \fIm88.ini\fR).
.TP
.I ~/.config/m88/roms/
Default ROM directory in user configuration mode.
.SH SEE ALSO
Project documentation in \fI@M88_QT_DOCDIR_FULL@\fR.
.SH COPYRIGHT
